<div class="usa-grid sign-up">
  <div class="sign-up-wrapper">
    <h1>Welcome to GDS Micro-purchase</h1>

    <div class="sign-up-welcome">
      Hi, <%= current_user.name %>, it looks like you’re new around here!
    </div>

    <div class="how-it-works-label">
      How it works
    </div>

    <div class="how-it-works">
      <p>
      None of the information stored in this application is considered proprietary or
      procurement-sensitive. Furthermore, all users who submit bids
      consent to the publication of their GitHub usernames, and bid
      amounts at the end of the auction. Bidders’ email
      addresses will not be disclosed and will only be used for
      micro-purchase-related communication on an as-needed basis.
      </p>

      <p>
      This platform is an experiment on micro-purchase opportunities in Government.
      Vendor organizations may have multiple user accounts registered on this
      micro-purchase platform and on GitHub. Please file a GitHub issue in this repo
      if you have any questions.
      </p>

      <p>
      Bidders must have a bank account in Singapore to receive payment for work done.
      </p>
    </div>

    <%= link_to 'Continue', profile_path, class: 'usa-button usa-button-outline' %>
  </div>
</div>
